OL,3,C'Never seen poverty like it' says
OL,4,Ccharity as Wales' first multibank opens
OL,6,FAn outreach worker says she has "never
OL,7,Fseen poverty like it", as Wales' first
OL,8,Fmultibank opens.
OL,10,FCwtch Mawr is Wales' first multibank
OL,11,Fin that redistributes unsold items to
OL,12,Fpeople in need for free.
OL,14,FA team of six sort through and
OL,15,Forganise all of the donations.
OL,16,FCharities and outreach workers then
OL,17,Fcollect and deliver the items to
OL,18,Fpeople they've been in contact with.
