OL,6,FNatasha Cardone, who is a senior
OL,7,Foutreach worker, commented on her
OL,8,Fexperience in recent months: "I live
OL,9,Fon a council estate and I've seen
OL,10,Fpoverty over the years. I've never
OL,11,Fseen as bad as it is now."
OL,13,FAccording to a survey by the Bevan
OL,14,FFoundation has found high levels ofThe
OL,15,Fleft-leaning think tank asked 1,029
OL,16,Fpeople about their standard of living.
OL,18,FThis multibank, run by the charity
OL,19,FFaith in Families, hopes to ease some
OL,20,Fof that burden.
