OL,6,FPhil Evans, the warehouse coordinator
OL,7,Fof Cwtch Mawr, he said: "We can get
OL,8,Fdeliveries of up to 30,000 items at a
OL,9,Ftime. Mostly from Amazon but other
OL,10,Fbusinesses too.
OL,12,F"We are giving out about 3,000 units a
OL,13,Fweek to local families in need. Which
OL,14,Fagain, when you think all of that
OL,15,Fwould end up in landfill rather than
OL,16,Fgoing to people when they're
OL,17,Fstruggling, is staggering really."
