OL,6,FCherrie Bija, the CEO of Faith in
OL,7,FFamilies, said: "Cwtch Mawr is a
OL,8,Fcollaboration of different sectors
OL,9,Fwanting to bring hope and support to
OL,10,Fthose who face some of the most
OL,11,Fchallenging situations in life, right
OL,12,Fhere in our communities.
OL,14,F"This big Welsh Hug can be
OL,15,Ftransformational for Swansea and South
OL,16,FWales From gifting children with brand-
OL,17,Fnew football boots so that they can
OL,18,Ftake part in their school team, to
OL,19,Fmaternity packs for new Mums so they
OL,20,Fcan have dignity going into hospital,
OL,21,Fthese things really matter.
